{
  "stem": "23498.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Escape.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Escaping.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you some small episode, which had a tremendous impact on me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was when we were led to the-- on foot, the whole group-- and in the middle of the road, and the looks on people-- on the Polish people faces, and how I felt about it, that I'll never forget as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a mixture with disgust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were looking terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, I was-- I was wearing boys' shoes, which were all hard and-- and broken, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we looked outrageous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people-- I couldn't forget that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was looking at the faces, and I thought, what would I give to be just a dog?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just a dog.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the one episode I wanted to mention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the thing was, when I was running and went to the house where-- where I was-- that I knew that she lives.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was standing on the staircase, on the last floor, and I thought, I don't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, it's still light.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have to be here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But people are walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They will ask me what I am doing here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Praga.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was next to the place where the Jews were working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the [INAUDIBLE] side, that was Praga.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Wilenska [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't recall-- Wilenska, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I-- I can hear the quick steps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I thought, what if she would-- because I could feel that she likes me, that girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was in the kitchen with the caretaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was doing some business with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, she was a young girl, only, but very [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
